  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Element Realm is a puzzle game with a magical adventure theme.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game tells the story of a wizard's adventure to the elemental world in order to protect the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as a wizard, visit different worlds, use different magic to solve massive levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Gorgeous world</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different elemental worlds have different characteristics, looking forward to your arrival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464740/extras/bb29d8e79ee0e27432e1da9f2a88c1b4.avif?t=1730789321\" width=512 height=512 /></span><u>Various magic</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various magics bring different effects and are used to solve different puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464740/extras/639d33730c24f4f65c272a41298d0d39.avif?t=1730789321\" width=128 height=128 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464740/extras/278f1b85cf70fbd83c7d632e2df39fb2.avif?t=1730789321\" width=128 height=128 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464740/extras/718624446ea4839c1cf1cf090b8d6cb9.avif?t=1730789321\" width=128 height=128 /></span><u>Massive levels</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ complex levels are waiting for your challenge, use your smart brain to slove them with the wizard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464740/extras/e50102d20ea3527443a62dfd381a0f20.avif?t=1730789321\" width=512 height=256 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464740/extras/5174c7059a77e2f0918603a2f5ec2a09.avif?t=1730789321\" width=512 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Element Realm is a puzzle game with a magical adventure theme.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game tells the story of a wizard's adventure to the elemental world in order to protect the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as a wizard, visit different worlds, use different magic to solve massive levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Gorgeous world</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different elemental worlds have different characteristics, looking forward to your arrival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464740/extras/bb29d8e79ee0e27432e1da9f2a88c1b4.avif?t=1730789321\" width=512 height=512 /></span><u>Various magic</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various magics bring different effects and are used to solve different puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464740/extras/639d33730c24f4f65c272a41298d0d39.avif?t=1730789321\" width=128 height=128 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464740/extras/278f1b85cf70fbd83c7d632e2df39fb2.avif?t=1730789321\" width=128 height=128 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464740/extras/718624446ea4839c1cf1cf090b8d6cb9.avif?t=1730789321\" width=128 height=128 /></span><u>Massive levels</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ complex levels are waiting for your challenge, use your smart brain to slove them with the wizard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2464740/extras/e50102d20ea3527443a62dfd381a0f20.a